column6: Hey I'm using the Mobile Academy app giving unlimited access to high quality courses on my mobile! They have a wide variety of courses from personal development, business and language courses to hobbies, book summeries and other general interest topics. It is free to try, so you can check it out yourself at: http://app.mobileacademy.com/
column12: Hei, saya sedang menggunakan aplikasi Mobile Academy yang memberikan akses tidak terbatas ke kursus berkualitas tinggi di perangkat seluler saya! Aplikasi ini punya beragam kursus, mulai dari kursus pengembangan pribadi, bisnis, dan bahasa hingga hobi, ringkasan buku, dan topik kepentingan umum. Ini gratis untuk dicoba, kalian dapat memeriksanya sendiri di: http://app.mobileacademy.com/
column22: เฮ้ ฉันกำลังใช้แอป Mobile Academy ที่ให้สิทธิ์การเข้าถึงหลักสูตรคุณภาพสูงไม่จำกัดผ่านทางมือถือของฉัน! พวกเขามีหลักสูตรให้บริการมากมายหลากหลายตั้งแต่หลักสูตรการพัฒนาตนเอง หลักสูตรธุรกิจและหลักสูตรภาษาไปจนถึงงานอดิเรก บทสรุปของหนังสือโดยย่อ และหัวข้อที่น่าสนใจอื่น ๆ  สามารถลองใช้บริการได้ฟรี คุณจึงสามารถลองดูได้ด้วยตัวคุณเองที่: http://app.mobileacademy.com/
column23: Hey cep telefonumdan yüksek kaliteli kurslara sınırsız erişim sağlayan Mobile Academy uygulamasını kullanıyorum! Denemek ücretsiz, bu yüzden kendiniz şu adresten bakabilirsiniz: http://app.mobileacademy.com/
column25: Này, tôi đang sử dụng ứng dụng Học viện Di động với quyền truy cập không giới hạn đến các khóa học chất lượng cao trên điện thoại di động của tôi! Họ có một loạt các khóa học từ phát triển bản thân, kinh doanh và ngôn ngữ đến sở thích, tóm lược sách và các chủ đề quan tâm khác. Bạn có thể học thử miễn phí, hãy xem thế nào: http://app.mobileacademy.com/
